metadata.name: 01 of 100 - Alice: The Prisoner - The Unclean
metadata.description:
"Living in a cage is a terrible thing, yes?  But what if you found that you didn't suffer in that dark place, but rather thrived?  Would you ever want out?  And if you did, what would you let slip into this world?" ~ Unknown

This is a 1:1, the first in a limited series of 100.  These characters are part of a shared universe.  There are two narrative projects already in development.  Owning one of these in the series will unlock a free copy of each, early access to both projects, and an exclusive reward for both projects.

Announcement of the upcoming projects will take place in March.  Specific dates will be announced soon.
